name: Jack Frost
text: It's August and you're fessed for warm weather, tank top and shorts, you shouldn't have to go get a sweatshirt before you go in for a sandwich. I made a comment to the manager that it was freezing in here guess what he say? "Not back here it's not" i went check the thermostat in the dining area and it was set at 63* food was ok.

name: Tim Cloutier
text: Counter guy greets customers with "are you ready?". How about a general hello instead? He then refused to answer when I asked him how he was doing today.  This location also uses pressed turkey instead of the real turkey D'Angelo is known for.
